@FinanceService.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5002
@token = your_jwt_token_here

### Получить все валюты
GET {{FinanceService.Api_HostAddress}}/api/currencies
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Получить избранные валюты
GET {{FinanceService.Api_HostAddress}}/api/favorites
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Добавить валюту в избранное по коду
POST {{FinanceService.Api_HostAddress}}/api/favorites
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "currencyCode": "EUR"
}

### Добавить валюту в избранное по id
POST {{FinanceService.Api_HostAddress}}/api/favorites
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "currencyId": "11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111"
}

### Health check
GET {{FinanceService.Api_HostAddress}}/health
Accept: application/json